Perfect natural look: totally undetectable even from close up, last all day all night through wind rain and sweat, will not smear or stain your skin or clothing, works for both men and women, unlike similar products on the mass market Looks21 Hair Fibers is a professional grade product, made from natural fibers from plants safe even for sensitive scalp, bonds to hair more securely does not require spray to glue fibers to your hair, free of animal ingredients synthetic dyes fillers and preservatives. When you sprinkle Looks21 Hair Fibers to your hair in the thinning area the fibers automatically cling to your hair like millions of tiny magnets your hair thickens instantly thus eliminating badspot or thinning area. Looks21 Hair Fibers is made from the following two ingredients: Moroccan Gossypium Herbaceum fiber and Natural mineral-based colorants. Moroccan Gossypium Herbaceum (also known as Levant cotton) is a plant that only grows in arid regions of Morocco. Fibers from this plant have surface optical properties that are very similar to human hair. This is one of the reasons why Looks21 Hair Fibers gives users perfectly natural look. Moroccan Gossypium Herbaceum fibers tend to negatively charged while human hair tends to be positively charged. Therefore Looks21 Hair Fibers bond to your hair 200% stronger than regular hair building fibers. Natural mineral-based colorants virgin moroccan gossypium herbaceum is grayish white. The fibers are dyed into various colors to match human hair colors. Thanks to the micro-structure of Gossypium Herbaceum its fiber can be easily dyed with mineral-based colorants - iron oxides harvested from nature. Looks21 Hair Fibers is the only 100% natural hair building fiber on the market it is free of synthetic dyes fillers preservatives and animal derivatives. It is hypoallergenic safe to use even on sensitive scalp.

Title: Aqua Floss Oral Irrigator and Water Floss - Optimum Oral Health
Description: Aqua floss is an oral irrigator for removing plaque bacteria and food debris present between teeth and below the gum line. It provides significant oral health benefit for people who wear braces, have diabetes, gum disease, dental implants, crowns and bridges since it becomes easy to maintain the gum health with Aqua Floss.• Aqua Floss has an ergonomic design and low profile tip emerging from a reservoir for water. Its push button uses air infusion technology for removing tooth deposits. It does not require batteries or cords for its operation.• The primary purpose of oral irrigation is to reduce harmful bacteria and therefore the risk and severity of periodontal disease. Studies have shown that daily oral irrigation has the potential to suppress periodontal pathogens located within the pocket. Oral irrigation has demonstrated a reduction in pro inflammatory mediators. Periodontal disease causing bacteria cause an increase in cytokine levels, which leads to bone resorption. Regular oral irrigation leads to a reduction in pro-inflammatory cytokines that leads to a slight, but significant, improvement in mild to moderate periodontal disease. In addition, oral irrigation has demonstrated a significant reduction in bleeding, gingivitis, periodontal pathogens and probing depths. The reduction in probing depth was minimal and may not be clinically relevant. Thus it appears that oral irrigation is a useful adjunct in suppressing and controlling periodontal disease and helps the dental clinician in improving the prognosis of periodontal disease.• It is well established that traditional brushing and flossing, or rinsing with anti microbials does not penetrate more than a Milli meter or two subgingivally. Since most of the active periodontal disease process occurs subgingivally, the necessity of cleaning to the base of the pocket becomes apparent. Fortunately, oral irrigator is easy to use in this scenario and is safe and effective.
